    "result": {"data":{"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"date":"2022-05-22","description":"","group":"git","pageTitle":"git教程","parentTitle":"二、git实操","path":"/git/git2-2","title":"2-2、规范化git commit格式"},"html":"<h2>本节介绍</h2>\n<p>良好的 commit 信息，可以让团队成员直观地了解项目的演进过程、快速定位需要的版本等</p>\n<p>具有一定规模的开源项目都有良好的 commit 规范，其中 Angular 的规范比较出名，咱们来学习一下</p>\n<img src=\"https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/e6c9d24egy1h2h1igbkt6j20ow0fwdih.jpg\" alt=\"image-20220522115212432\"  />\n<h2>一、Angular的commit规范</h2>\n<p>Angular commit 的规范格式如下：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-html line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>type</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>(<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>scope</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>):<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>subject</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n// 空一行\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n// 空一行\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>footer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>只有 type（提交类型） 和 subject（提交描述） 是必须的，其余部分可选</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h4>type —— 提交类型（必填）</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>feat：新增 feature</li>\n<li>fix：修补 bug</li>\n<li>perf：更改代码，性能优化</li>\n<li>refactor：代码重构</li>\n<li>test：新增、修改测试用例</li>\n<li>build：修改依赖项</li>\n<li>docs：仅修改了文档，如 readme.md</li>\n<li>style：仅对代码格式修改，如缩紧、空格、缺失的分号等</li>\n<li>release：发布新版本</li>\n<li>ci：对CI配置文件或脚本进行了修改</li>\n<li>chore：其他修改，不在上述类型中的修改</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>scope —— 影响范围（可选）</h4>\n<p>此次 commit 影响的范围，如：views、components、utils...</p>\n<h4>subject —— 描述（必填）</h4>\n<p>此次 commit 的描述，小于100个词</p>\n<h4>body —— 详细描述（可选）</h4>\n<p>此次 commit 的详细描述，多行、长度不限</p>\n<h4>footer —— 备注（可选）</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>breaking changes：本次提交是否有不兼容之前版本的 API 或 环境变量</li>\n<li>issues：如果此次提交的目的是修改 issue 的话，需要在页脚引用该 issue，例如 fix #123</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>二、使用commitizen生成Angular规范的commit</h2>\n<p>上面提到的 Angular 规范纯手写有点麻烦，<strong>commitizen 工具可以帮助开发人员生成 Angular 规范的 commit 内容</strong></p>\n<p>为统一 commit 格式，所有团队开发人员都应该安装此工具</p>\n<h3>2-1、安装commitizen</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token comment\"># conventional-changelog 是 commitizen 的依赖</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> -g commitizen conventional-changelog conventional-changelog-cli\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 安装完成后，检查是否安装成功</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">ls</span> -g -depth<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p><img src=\"https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/e6c9d24ely1h2hcv5oubxj20os0an75b.jpg\" alt=\"image-20220522182459564\"></p>\n<br>\n<h3>2-2、配置conventional</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token comment\"># 如果项目中没有 pages.json 文件执行此命令，否则请忽略</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">npm</span> init --yes\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 设置 Angular 的 commit</span>\ncommitizen init cz-conventional-changelog --save --save-exact\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 测试配置是否成功，执行下面的命令生成 CHANGELOG.md 文件即配置成功</span>\nconventional-changelog -p angular -i CHANGELOG.md -s</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<br>\n<h3>2-3、使用git cz代替git commit</h3>\n<p>凡是用到 git commit 命令的地方， 改为 <strong>git cz</strong></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token comment\"># 其他命令，正常使用</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">git</span> <span class=\"token function\">add</span> <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">.</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># git cz 代替 git commit 命令</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 执行后会出现设置 commit 的交互界面</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">git</span> cz\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 其他命令，正常使用</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">git</span> push</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>根据交互提示，完善 commit 内容即可</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/e6c9d24ely1h2hdr8ltz9j20os08oq4b.jpg\" alt=\"image-20220522185551846\"></p>\n<br>\n<h3>2-4、查看commit信息</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token function\">git</span> log</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p><img src=\"https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/e6c9d24ely1h2hehptotsj20os07awf1.jpg\" alt=\"image-20220522192118973\"></p>\n<h2>快速回顾</h2>\n<p>在本节中，您学习了</p>\n<ul>\n<li>了解了 Angular 的 commit 规范</li>\n<li>掌握了 commitizen 工具的使用方法</li>\n</ul>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%E6%9C%AC%E8%8A%82%E4%BB%8B%E7%BB%8D\">本节介绍</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%E4%B8%80angular%E7%9A%84commit%E8%A7%84%E8%8C%83\">一、Angular的commit规范</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%E4%BA%8C%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8commitizen%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90angular%E8%A7%84%E8%8C%83%E7%9A%84commit\">二、使用commitizen生成Angular规范的commit</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E5%9B%9E%E9%A1%BE\">快速回顾</a></li>\n</ul>"},"allMarkdownRemark":{"group":[{"edges":[{"node":{"frontmatter":{"path":"/git/git1-1","title":"1-1、安装git","parentTitle":"一、git入门","pageTitle":"git教程","group":"git"},"id":"94d4ea74-6b56-52e1-b3f4-fabbd27b0e29"},"next":{"frontmatter":{"title":"1-2、第一次用git要知道的","path":"/git/git1-2"}},"previous":null},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"path":"/git/git1-2","title":"1-2、第一次用git要知道的","parentTitle":"一、git入门","pageTitle":"git教程","group":"git"},"id":"767a32cd-5ca6-58f8-a9ff-7f65407aae7e"},"next":{"frontmatter":{"title":"1-3、搭建gitee远程仓库","path":"/git/git1-3"}},"previous":{"frontmatter":{"title":"1-1、安装git","path":"/git/git1-1"}}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"path":"/git/git1-3","title":"1-3、搭建gitee远程仓库","parentTitle":"一、git入门","pageTitle":"git教程","group":"git"},"id":"b996fc4f-a791-5ee9-96d2-b0bc3286775c"},"next":{"frontmatter":{"title":"1-4、搭建本地仓库","path":"/git/git1-4"}},"previous":{"frontmatter":{"title":"1-2、第一次用git要知道的","path":"/git/git1-2"}}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"path":"/git/git1-4","title":"1-4、搭建本地仓库","parentTitle":"一、git入门","pageTitle":"git教程","group":"git"},"id":"75c85948-5d76-5d6c-ba2f-a15b300f86c7"},"next":{"frontmatter":{"title":"1-5、本地同步到远程仓库","path":"/git/git1-5"}},"previous":{"frontmatter":{"title":"1-3、搭建gitee远程仓库","path":"/git/git1-3"}}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"path":"/git/git1-5","title":"1-5、本地同步到远程仓库","parentTitle":"一、git入门","pageTitle